## 4ï¸âƒ£ Binary Search ğŸ”

### **When to use**

* Sorted data
* â€œFind minimum / maximum possible valueâ€
* Problems where answer space is sorted

### **How it works**

* Divide search space into half
* Check mid â†’ move left or right

### **Common problems**

* Search in sorted array
* Minimum capacity / speed problems
* First & last occurrence

